# Icons & Assets

## ⚠️ CRITICAL RULE: NEVER Generate SVG Code

**NEVER create SVG markup from scratch.** This wastes tokens and creates maintenance issues.

**ALWAYS use icon libraries instead.**

## Recommended Icon Libraries

### Web (Choose ONE per project)

#### 1. Font Awesome (Most Popular)
```html
<!-- CDN -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">

<!-- Usage -->
<i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i>
<i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i>
<i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
```

**Pros**: Huge library (2000+ icons), widely known, good documentation
**Sizes**: 16px, 20px, 24px, 32px via classes (`fa-sm`, `fa-lg`, `fa-2x`)

#### 2. Heroicons (Tailwind Ecosystem)
```html
<!-- Install: npm install @heroicons/react -->
<!-- React -->
import { UserIcon, HeartIcon, MagnifyingGlassIcon } from '@heroicons/react/24/outline'

<UserIcon className="h-6 w-6" />
```

**Pros**: Beautiful, modern, 2 styles (outline/solid), optimized SVG components
**Sizes**: 16px, 20px, 24px

#### 3. Lucide Icons (Modern Alternative)
```html
<!-- CDN -->
<script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

<!-- Usage -->
<i data-lucide="user"></i>
<i data-lucide="heart"></i>
<i data-lucide="search"></i>

<script>
  lucide.createIcons();
</script>
```

**Pros**: Clean, consistent, actively maintained, 1000+ icons
**Sizes**: Customizable via CSS

#### 4. Material Symbols (Google)
```html
<!-- CDN -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined">

<!-- Usage -->
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">favorite</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">search</span>
```

**Pros**: Google's design system, variable font, 2500+ icons
**Sizes**: Customizable via font-size

#### 5. Bootstrap Icons
```html
<!-- CDN -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">

<!-- Usage -->
<i class="bi bi-person"></i>
<i class="bi bi-heart"></i>
<i class="bi bi-search"></i>
```

**Pros**: 2000+ icons, works without Bootstrap, clean design

### React/Vue/Svelte Components

#### React Icons (Universal)
```jsx
// Install: npm install react-icons
import { FaUser, FaHeart, FaSearch } from 'react-icons/fa'
import { HiUser, HiHeart, HiSearch } from 'react-icons/hi2'
import { BiUser, BiHeart, BiSearch } from 'react-icons/bi'

<FaUser size={24} />
<HiUser className="h-6 w-6" />
```

**Pros**: All major icon sets in one package, tree-shakeable

#### Vue/Svelte
Use the same libraries via CDN or component wrappers.

### iOS (Native)

#### SF Symbols (Apple)
```swift
// SwiftUI
Image(systemName: "person")
Image(systemName: "heart")
Image(systemName: "magnifyingglass")

// Sizes
.font(.system(size: 20))
.imageScale(.small) // .medium, .large
```

**Pros**: 5000+ symbols, native, automatic theming, variable

### Android (Native)

#### Material Icons
```kotlin
// Jetpack Compose
Icon(Icons.Default.Person, contentDescription = "User")
Icon(Icons.Default.Favorite, contentDescription = "Heart")
Icon(Icons.Default.Search, contentDescription = "Search")

// Sizes
modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp)
```

**Pros**: Native, Material Design, automatic theming

## Icon Usage Guidelines

### Sizing

#### Standard Sizes
- **16px**: Small UI elements, inline with text
- **20px**: Medium UI elements, buttons
- **24px**: Default size, navigation, toolbars
- **32px**: Large buttons, prominent actions
- **48px**: Hero icons, empty states

#### Implementation
```css
/* CSS */
.icon-sm { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
.icon-md { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
.icon-lg { width: 24px; height: 24px; }
.icon-xl { width: 32px; height: 32px; }
.icon-2xl { width: 48px; height: 48px; }
```

### Color

#### Use Current Color
```css
/* Icons inherit text color */
.icon {
  color: currentColor;
}
```

#### Semantic Colors
```html
<!-- Success -->
<i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-600"></i>

<!-- Error -->
<i class="fa-solid fa-xmark text-red-600"></i>

<!-- Warning -->
<i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-orange-600"></i>

<!-- Info -->
<i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info text-blue-600"></i>
```

### Accessibility

#### Always Include Labels
```html
<!-- Screen reader text -->
<button aria-label="Close dialog">
  <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark" aria-hidden="true"></i>
</button>

<!-- Or visible text -->
<button>
  <i class="fa-solid fa-save" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  <span>Save</span>
</button>
```

#### Hide Decorative Icons
```html
<i class="fa-solid fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
```

### Common Icon Mappings

#### Actions
- **Close/Delete**: `xmark`, `close`, `x`
- **Add/Create**: `plus`, `add`
- **Edit**: `pen`, `pencil`, `edit`
- **Save**: `floppy-disk`, `save`
- **Search**: `magnifying-glass`, `search`
- **Filter**: `filter`, `funnel`
- **Settings**: `gear`, `settings`, `cog`
- **Menu**: `bars`, `menu`
- **More**: `ellipsis-vertical`, `more-vert`

#### Navigation
- **Home**: `house`, `home`
- **Back**: `arrow-left`, `chevron-left`
- **Forward**: `arrow-right`, `chevron-right`
- **Up**: `arrow-up`, `chevron-up`
- **Down**: `arrow-down`, `chevron-down`
- **External**: `arrow-up-right-from-square`, `external-link`

#### Status
- **Success**: `check`, `check-circle`
- **Error**: `xmark`, `exclamation-circle`
- **Warning**: `triangle-exclamation`, `warning`
- **Info**: `circle-info`, `info`
- **Loading**: `spinner`, `circle-notch` (with animation)

#### User/Social
- **User**: `user`, `person`
- **Users**: `users`, `people`
- **Profile**: `user-circle`, `account-circle`
- **Heart/Like**: `heart`
- **Star/Favorite**: `star`
- **Share**: `share-nodes`, `share`
- **Comment**: `comment`, `message`

#### File/Document
- **File**: `file`, `description`
- **Folder**: `folder`
- **Download**: `download`, `arrow-down-to-line`
- **Upload**: `upload`, `arrow-up-from-line`
- **Attachment**: `paperclip`, `attach-file`
- **Image**: `image`, `photo`

## Image Assets

### Use Placeholder Services

#### For Development
```html
<!-- Unsplash (real photos) -->
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x600/?business" alt="Business photo">

<!-- Placeholder.com (solid colors) -->
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/0078D4/FFFFFF?text=Product+Image" alt="Product">

<!-- Picsum (random photos) -->
<img src="https://picsum.photos/800/600" alt="Random photo">
```

#### For Production
- Use a CDN (Cloudinary, Imgix)
- Optimize images (WebP, AVIF)
- Provide multiple sizes (srcset)
- Include proper alt text

### Logo Placeholders

```html
<!-- Simple text logo -->
<div class="logo">
  <span class="font-bold text-xl">Acme</span>
</div>

<!-- Or use icon + text -->
<div class="logo flex items-center gap-2">
  <i class="fa-solid fa-cube text-2xl text-blue-600"></i>
  <span class="font-bold text-xl">Acme</span>
</div>
```

## Best Practices

### Do:
- ✅ Use established icon libraries
- ✅ Choose ONE library per project
- ✅ Use standard sizes (16, 20, 24, 32, 48px)
- ✅ Include aria-label for icon-only buttons
- ✅ Use aria-hidden="true" for decorative icons
- ✅ Make icons inherit text color (currentColor)
- ✅ Provide text labels alongside icons when possible
- ✅ Use semantic colors (green=success, red=error)

### Don't:
- ❌ Generate SVG code from scratch
- ❌ Mix multiple icon libraries
- ❌ Use inconsistent icon sizes
- ❌ Forget accessibility labels
- ❌ Use icons as only indicator (add text)
- ❌ Use decorative icons without aria-hidden
- ❌ Hardcode icon colors (use CSS)
- ❌ Use tiny icons (<16px)

