## Summary

**NEVER generate SVG code.** Always use:
1. Font Awesome (most popular)
2. Heroicons (modern, Tailwind)
3. Lucide (clean, consistent)
4. Material Symbols (Google)
5. Bootstrap Icons (versatile)

Choose ONE library per project and use it consistently.
